| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-5365 — Recovery Inhibition (direwolf)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: f722f441-3f60-5c97-95a2-a91f97ed2f2f"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
